            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPRR585YZ%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPRR585YZ%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22document%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22Tribunal%20de%20Justi%C3%A7a%20da%20Uni%C3%A3o%20Europeia%20-%202006%20-%20Ac%C3%B3rd%C3%A3o%20no%20processo%20C-168_05%20(Mostaza%20Claro%20v%20Centro%20M%C3%B3vil%20Milenium%20SL)%22%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22TribunalJusticaUniao%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 05:56:48)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FF7EX4S5B%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%222IVXVLRE%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%222%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A1%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B44.095%2C585.344%2C220.238%2C593.841%5D%2C%5B233.04%2C585.344%2C409.183%2C593.841%5D%2C%5B44.095%2C574.752%2C220.237%2C583.06%5D%2C%5B233.04%2C574.752%2C409.182%2C583.06%5D%2C%5B44.095%2C564.148%2C220.238%2C572.456%5D%2C%5B233.04%2C563.895%2C335.216%2C572.392%5D%2C%5B44.095%2C553.29%2C220.237%2C561.787%5D%2C%5B44.095%2C542.698%2C220.24%2C551.006%5D%2C%5B44.095%2C531.841%2C220.237%2C540.337%5D%2C%5B44.095%2C521.248%2C220.237%2C529.557%5D%2C%5B44.095%2C510.391%2C220.238%2C518.888%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPRR585YZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%222%22%7D%7D\">\u201cDirective 93/13, concerning unfair terms in consumer contracts, must be interpreted as meaning that a national court seised of an action for annulment of an arbitration award must determine whether the arbitration agreement is void and annul that award where that agreement contains an unfair term, even though the consumer has not\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPRR585YZ%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%222%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">\u201cTribunal de Justi\u00e7a da Uni\u00e3o Europeia - 2006 - Ac\u00f3rd\u00e3o no processo C-168_05 (Mostaza Claro v Centro M\u00f3vil Milenium SL)\u201d, p. 2</span>)</span> Este caso \u00e9 muito relevante e citado recorrentemente em muitos dos trabalhos. \u00c9 uma fonte prim\u00e1ria e sua importancia tamb\u00e9m reside no fato de que a an\u00e1lise do texto pode indicar se o direito p\u00e1trio ao tomar de emprestimo algumas nomenclaturas e conceitos os fazem nos mesmos termos enunciados na controversia em quest\u00e3o.</p>\n</div></div>",
