            "item_title": "Anota\u00e7\u00f5es (20/11/2025, 05:56:32)",
            "item_type": "note",
            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPSQ3E3T6%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPSQ3E3T6%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22document%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22Tribunal%20de%20Justi%C3%A7a%20da%20Uni%C3%A3o%20Europeia%20-%202009%20-%20Ac%C3%B3rd%C3%A3o%20no%20processo%20C-40_08%20(Asturcom%20Telecomunicaciones)%22%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22TribunalJusticaUniaob%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 05:56:32)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FKN7J2MUQ%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22CKX9NLSM%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%229604%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A2%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B45.354%2C456.531%2C413.484%2C466.086%5D%2C%5B45.354%2C445.023%2C413.474%2C454.578%5D%2C%5B45.354%2C433.515%2C303.728%2C443.07%5D%2C%5B25.512%2C377.784%2C413.369%2C387.339%5D%2C%5B45.354%2C366.276%2C413.516%2C375.831%5D%2C%5B45.354%2C354.768%2C413.474%2C364.323%5D%2C%5B45.354%2C343.26%2C413.39%2C352.815%5D%2C%5B45.354%2C331.752%2C237.903%2C341.307%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPSQ3E3T6%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%229604%22%7D%7D\">\u201cO pedido de decis\u00e3o prejudicial tem por objecto a interpreta\u00e7\u00e3o da Directiva 93/13/CEE do Conselho, de 5 de Abril de 1993, relativa \u00e0s cl\u00e1usulas abusivas nos contratos celebrados com os consumidores (JO L 95, p. 29). 2 Este pedido foi apresentado no \u00e2mbito de um pedido de execu\u00e7\u00e3o de uma decis\u00e3o arbitral definitiva que op\u00f5e a sociedade Asturcom Telecomunicaciones SL (a seguir \u00abAsturcom\u00bb) a C. Rodr\u00edguez Nogueira a prop\u00f3sito do pagamento de import\u00e2ncias devidas em execu\u00e7\u00e3o de um contrato de presta\u00e7\u00e3o de servi\u00e7os de telefonia m\u00f3vel que a referida sociedade concluiu com esta \u00faltima.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FPSQ3E3T6%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%229604%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">\u201cTribunal de Justi\u00e7a da Uni\u00e3o Europeia - 2009 - Ac\u00f3rd\u00e3o no processo C-40_08 (Asturcom Telecomunicaciones)\u201d, p. 9604</span>)</span></p>\n</div></div>",
