            "item_type": "note",
            "item_note": "<div class=\"zotero-note znv1\"><div data-citation-items=\"%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FVIUFI2WU%22%5D%2C%22itemData%22%3A%7B%22id%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FVIUFI2WU%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22document%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22Unimar%20-%202020%20-%20Direito%20civil_%20Teoria%20geral%20dos%20contratos%20e%20contratos%20em%20esp%C3%A9cie%22%2C%22citation-key%22%3A%22Unimar2020Direito%22%7D%7D%5D\" data-schema-version=\"9\"><h1>Anota\u00e7\u00f5es<br/>(20/11/2025, 05:56:23)</h1>\n<p><span class=\"highlight\" data-annotation=\"%7B%22attachmentURI%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FRIP259ZS%22%2C%22annotationKey%22%3A%22VT79TLDF%22%2C%22color%22%3A%22%23fff6cc%22%2C%22pageLabel%22%3A%22145%22%2C%22position%22%3A%7B%22pageIndex%22%3A0%2C%22rects%22%3A%5B%5B102.738%2C449.188%2C511.757%2C461.353%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C433.607%2C511.738%2C445.772%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C421.657%2C511.727%2C433.711%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C402.445%2C511.738%2C414.61%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C386.864%2C511.714%2C399.029%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C371.283%2C511.755%2C383.448%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C355.702%2C511.714%2C367.867%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C340.121%2C511.741%2C352.286%5D%2C%5B102.738%2C328.171%2C261.508%2C340.225%5D%5D%7D%2C%22citationItem%22%3A%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FVIUFI2WU%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%22145%22%7D%7D\">\u201cRESUMO: A arbitragem \u00e9 uma forma de resolu\u00e7\u00e3o de con\uf002flitos que est\u00e1 presente em grande parte dos sistemas jur\u00eddicos. Deve ser analisada na sua fun\u00e7\u00e3o de aplicar o direito e paci\uf001ficar a sociedade, dentro de um contexto de acesso \u00e0 justi\u00e7a. Atrav\u00e9s da arbitragem, em raz\u00e3o de algumas das suas caracter\u00edsticas, \u00e9 poss\u00edvel promover a distribui\u00e7\u00e3o da justi\u00e7a de forma mais r\u00e1pida e efetiva, realizando plenamente algumas das expectativas da sociedade de acesso a uma ordem jur\u00eddica justa. Palavras-chave: Arbitragem. Vantagens da Arbitragem. Acesso \u00e0 Justi\u00e7a. Jurisdi\u00e7\u00e3o e suas \uf001finalidades.\u201d</span> <span class=\"citation\" data-citation=\"%7B%22citationItems%22%3A%5B%7B%22uris%22%3A%5B%22http%3A%2F%2Fzotero.org%2Fusers%2Flocal%2FZBIgIGVI%2Fitems%2FVIUFI2WU%22%5D%2C%22locator%22%3A%22145%22%7D%5D%2C%22properties%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\">(<span class=\"citation-item\">\u201cUnimar - 2020 - Direito civil_ Teoria geral dos contratos e contratos em esp\u00e9cie\u201d, p. 145</span>)</span> O trabalho pode ser \u00fatil para definir o ponto de partida de an\u00e1lises teleol\u00f3gicas, j\u00e1 que fixando quest\u00f5es propedeuticas, ajuda a balizar o alcan\u00e7amento dos fins da lei, ou crit\u00e9rios para determina\u00e7\u00e3o de quando o ecossistema econ\u00f4mico subverte os fins consttitucionais para apresentar um resultado diverso e violador de direitos.</p>\n</div></div>",
